data.description: Serenity Surrounds this home on 5.37 acres of level land with the possibilities being endless. Bring your livestock, horses, chickens, side by sides.  The Sunset and sunrise views from this property are absolutely spectacular.  So much potential here. Completely fenced property with backyard wood fencing for a little more privacy, wood deck and mature shade trees. Split floor plan with extra-large primary bedroom and bath, with large soaking tub and separate walk-in shower.  So much storage space in kitchen with breakfast bar, refrigerator, stove and microwave.  DO NOT USE GPS, DO NOT GO WITHOUT APPOINTMENT.
